21 motor vehicle and is engaged, and the motor vehicle is operating as a fully
22 autonomous vehicle as defined in KRS 186.760, the:
23 (a) Owner of the motor vehicle is considered the operator of the fully autonomous
24 vehicle and shall comply with applicable traffic or motor vehicle laws,
25 regardless of whether the owner is physically present in the vehicle while the
26 vehicle is operating; and
27 (b) Automated driving system is considered to be licensed to operate the vehicle
